out...

05:57.357 --> 05:59.097
"...what mine is all about.

05:59.097 --> 06:03.188
"Oh, Sam, so many emotions
are surfacing as I write this."

06:04.407 --> 06:06.191
Where is she, Mr. Green?

06:06.191 --> 06:08.672
