if you didn't talk for a while.

06:08.672 --> 06:11.545
Let me finish this off.

06:11.545 --> 06:14.025
"You're my best friend in the
world, Sam...

06:14.025 --> 06:16.593
"...so you must know
that this is the way I am.

06:16.593 --> 06:18.595
