thing.

07:07.818 --> 07:08.993
I'm sure you are.

07:58.303 --> 07:59.696
Honey!

07:59.696 --> 08:01.742
What is it?

08:01.742 --> 08:03.700
Can you get that?

08:03.700 --> 08:05.049
I'm taking a nap.

08:05.049 --> 08:06.050
I'm in the bath.

08:06.050 --> 08:08.488
All right.

08:08.488 --> 08:11.447
I hear you, God damn it!

08:11.447 --> 08:13.057
Are you OK?

08:13.057 --> 08:14.842
What's this table doing here?

08:14.842 --> 08:16.713
This better be goddamn good!

08:16.713 --> 08:18.976
You're ruining my beauty sleep!

08:18.976 --> 08:22.893
Damn you! Lay off the buzzer!

08:22.893 --> 08:24.504
Who is it?

08:26.288 --> 08:28.029
No problem here.

08:28.682 --> 08:30.031
Who is it?

10:33.371 --> 10:35.025
Morning, everybody.

10:35.025 --> 10:37.071
Morning, Linda. Morning,
Tarzan.

10:38.855 --> 10:41.162
We are...

10:41.162 --> 10:43.730
...six minutes later than
yesterday.

10:43.730 --> 10:47.168
That's six, carry the two.
Good.

10:52.695 --> 10:54.349
Ah, there.

10:54.349 --> 10:55.785
See that?

10:55.785 --> 10:58.353
Medium smile, no teeth.

11:01.051 --> 11:02.879
Don't forget the vase.

11:02.879 --> 11:04.359
Got to get it perfectly
centered.

11:04.359 --> 11:06.448
There? No.

11:06.448 --> 11:07.884
There? No.

11:12.410 --> 11:14.369
One more. Why not?

11:16.676 --> 11:19.417
Annoying, isn't it, honey?

11:19.679 --> 11:22.246
Grin all you want, monkey man.

11:22.594 --> 11:25.728
All you are is a passing
meteor shower.

11:25.728 --> 11:27.208
You'll be gone soon enough.

11:29.079 --> 11:30.864
I feel sorry for you, you poor
bastard.

11:50.753 --> 11:52.668
Carl, it's me, Sam.

11:52.668 --> 11:54.017
Calm down. I'm fine.

11:54.017 --> 11:55.453
I'm still in New York.

11:57.238 --> 11:59.762
We're great. Linda's very
happy.

11:59.762 --> 12:02.547
We may stay a while. We're
very busy.

12:02.547 --> 12:03.592
There's lots to do.

12:05.899 --> 12:09.293
Listen, Carl, I need you to sell
my truck.

12:09.293 --> 12:11.034
Whatever you can get for it.

12:11.034 --> 12:14.168
I'm just a little short of cash
right now.

12:21.741 --> 12:24.004
I'm still here.

12:24.004 --> 12:25.657
Listen, Carl,
there's something else I need...

12:25.657 --> 12:28.617
...and Professor Wells
doesn't have to know about it.

13:21.975 --> 13:24.891
Hey, Linda. How you doing?

13:27.894 --> 13:30.157
You want to hear something
funny?

13:30.157 --> 13:33.377
I saw this on the news before I
came out.

13:33.377 --> 13:35.858
Fainting goats. I'm not making
this up.

13:35.858 --> 13:37.207
There's this breed of goats.

13:37.207 --> 13:40.080
I don't know why, but...

13:40.080 --> 13:43.257
...they faint at the slightest
thing.

13:43.257 --> 13:47.914
If they hear a loud noise
or a gun goes off...

13:47.914 --> 13:52.005
...they black out, fall right
over,
one after the other.

13:58.054 --> 14:00.361
I thought you'd like that.

15:20.049 --> 15:21.790
Get off.

15:40.852 --> 15:42.985
I don't even have a chart for
that.

15:47.381 --> 15:48.512
Get over here.

15:49.731 --> 15:50.775
Gotcha!

17:04.762 --> 17:06.329
Get away from here!

17:11.204 --> 17:14.903
I'm warning you! I have a gun!

17:14.903 --> 17:15.947
Oh, shit.

17:33.008 --> 17:35.619
What the hell are you?

17:49.807 --> 17:51.722
What do you want? Who are you?

17:51.722 --> 17:54.595
