17:54.595 --> 17:56.945
I live here. What do you want?

17:59.948 --> 18:02.081
I asked you a question.

18:08.478 --> 18:10.480
Don't touch that.

18:10.480 --> 18:12.308
Get away from that.

18:15.485 --> 18:17.792
Who the hell are you? What do
you want?

18:19.054 --> 18:20.316
They'll hear you.

18:20.316 --> 18:22.492
What are you talking about?

18:22.666 --> 18:26.366
Your little Goldilocks and my
ex-fiancé.

18:32.633 --> 18:34.722
Hold it.

18:34.722 --> 18:38.595
Are you saying that guy,
that thing over there...?

18:43.861 --> 18:45.298
-What's your name?
-Mike.

18:46.386 --> 18:48.997
-What's your name, Mike?
-Sam.

18:48.997 --> 18:50.694
I'm Maggie.

18:50.694 --> 18:52.522
I'll be staying here a while.

19:07.233 --> 19:10.236
I sleep naked.
It's the only way I'm
comfortable.

19:10.236 --> 19:12.020
So don't think of it as a
come-on...

19:12.020 --> 19:13.326
...because if you so much as
breathe
in my direction...

19:13.326 --> 19:15.415
...will nail your willy to that
beam.

19:17.068 --> 19:19.984
Don't mess with my stuff,
don't get in my way...

19:19.984 --> 19:23.205
...and I'm sure we'll get along
fine.

19:23.205 --> 19:24.511
Nighty-night.

20:29.532 --> 20:31.534
What is all this stuff?

20:31.534 --> 20:33.623
Bugging equipment, cactus.

20:33.623 --> 20:35.451
Like listening bugging?

20:35.451 --> 20:36.931
Bugging who?

20:39.542 --> 20:40.935
Take a wild guess.

20:42.806 --> 20:44.939
Why would anyone want to do
that?

20:44.939 --> 20:46.941
'Cause I want to hear
what goes on in there.

20:46.941 --> 20:48.682
Don't you want to hear
what goes on in there?

20:48.682 --> 20:49.683
No, I do not.

20:49.683 --> 20:51.293
Why not?

20:51.293 --> 20:54.209
'Cause that would be
an invasion of her privacy.

20:54.209 --> 20:56.255
Excuse me, Mr. Video.

20:56.255 --> 20:57.821
That's not a video.

20:57.821 --> 20:59.301
It's a camera obscura.

20:59.301 --> 21:00.824
It's pure light.

21:00.824 --> 21:02.304
I'm not spying.

21:02.304 --> 21:04.785
I just want to be with her.

21:04.785 --> 21:07.527
That's completely different.

21:07.527 --> 21:09.180
I know how you feel.

21:09.180 --> 21:11.487
You want him back so badly
that you can't stand it.

21:11.487 --> 21:13.315
It's like your guts
are twisting around inside.

21:13.315 --> 21:15.186
But bugging their apartment....

21:15.186 --> 21:17.363
What?

21:17.363 --> 21:20.061
I don't want him back.
I want him vaporized.

21:21.149 --> 21:22.977
Extinguished!

21:22.977 --> 21:24.848
When I'm done with him...

21:24.848 --> 21:27.808
...he'll be a twitchy little
stain on the floor.

21:32.682 --> 21:34.118
Is that what you're doing?

21:34.118 --> 21:36.817
You're waiting
for her to leave him for you?

21:36.817 --> 21:37.992
Absolutely.

21:37.992 --> 21:39.559
Have you seen him?

21:39.559 --> 21:41.822
He is irrelevant.
Linda and I are soul mates.

21:41.822 --> 21:44.172
This is just a passing phase.

21:44.172 --> 21:47.044
They're going to break up
tonight.
I know it.

21:47.044 --> 21:48.176
I'm listening.

21:48.176 --> 21:50.700
I'm an astronomer.

21:50.700 --> 21:52.876
It's my job to find patterns in
things...

21:52.876 --> 21:55.270
...that seem completely random.

21:55.270 --> 21:58.273
I found a pattern.

21:58.273 --> 22:00.884
It's all in the data.

22:00.884 --> 22:02.538
The data.

22:02.538 --> 22:04.453
This data.

22:04.453 --> 22:07.108
"Mutual feeding activity."

22:07.108 --> 22:09.066
It's the number of times
that Linda and
what's-his-name...

22:09.066 --> 22:10.503
...feed each other.

22:10.503 --> 22:13.157
