22:13.157 --> 22:15.943
Kisses, hugs, smiles, fights.

22:15.943 --> 22:17.031
They fight?

22:17.031 --> 22:18.293
Not yet.

22:18.293 --> 22:20.730
Long looks, whispering,
shouting.

22:20.730 --> 22:21.862
They shout?

22:21.862 --> 22:23.254
You're missing the point.

22:23.254 --> 22:25.822
Tonight there's going to be a
fight.

22:25.822 --> 22:27.520
They are going to break up...

22:27.520 --> 22:29.652
...and I'm going to be right
here for her.

22:29.652 --> 22:31.785
Tonight this will all be over...

22:31.785 --> 22:35.397
...so you might as well start
packing
your bags.

22:35.397 --> 22:40.750
That is the most pathetic thing
I've ever heard.

22:40.750 --> 22:42.317
I don't mean that trivially.

22:42.317 --> 22:43.927
I'm a photographer.
I've seen a lot of things.

22:43.927 --> 22:47.104
I once took pictures
of a man who ate his own legs...

22:47.104 --> 22:48.802
...and you would be the black
sheep
of that family.

22:48.802 --> 22:51.761
What's your evil plan?
Squirt him with squirt guns?

22:51.761 --> 22:53.937
Throw rotten strawberries at
him?

22:53.937 --> 22:55.548
You looked in my satchel?

22:55.548 --> 22:57.767
Yeah. Call a cop.

22:57.767 --> 23:00.814
You are a strange, tragic little
man.

23:00.814 --> 23:03.556
Say what you want.
Linda and I are in love.

23:03.556 --> 23:04.948
Except for her boning my
boyfriend...

23:04.948 --> 23:06.863
...you guys are the perfect
couple.

23:06.863 --> 23:09.344
Listen, Catwoman, at the end of
the day...

23:09.344 --> 23:12.129
...she is coming back to me,
and we're going to be happy.

23:12.129 --> 23:14.001
And where are you going to be?

23:14.001 --> 23:16.351
All alone somewhere,
hatching some little revenge
scheme.

23:19.485 --> 23:21.312
Let me tell you something, Sam.

23:21.312 --> 23:24.664
Listen very carefully. Are you
listening?

23:24.664 --> 23:26.622
The only way that girl
is coming back to you...

23:26.622 --> 23:28.494
...is if a blast of semen
catapults her...

23:28.494 --> 23:31.018
...across the street
and through the window.

23:34.282 --> 23:36.415
I want you out.

23:36.415 --> 23:38.155
Not going to happen.

23:38.155 --> 23:39.809
I was here first.

23:39.809 --> 23:42.159
Put me down for half the rent
and get out of my face.

23:46.773 --> 23:49.384
I wouldn't do that if I were
you.

23:49.384 --> 23:50.385
