Pictures of you and Linda.

1:24:30.239 --> 1:24:32.415
I told you I want him finished
off.

1:24:32.415 --> 1:24:34.460
It doesn't have anything to do
with you and me.

1:24:34.460 --> 1:24:36.593
I told you, stay out of my way.

1:24:40.031 --> 1:24:41.728
That's it?

1:24:41.728 --> 1:24:43.948
If that's what you want,
that's what it's going to take.

1:24:43.948 --> 1:24:47.038
Fine. Let's get it the hell
over with, then.

1:25:09.495 --> 1:25:11.976
Thank God, Mike. Thank God
you're back.

1:25:11.976 --> 1:25:13.586
Scratch me, Mike, please.

1:25:13.586 --> 1:25:15.806
Scratch my chest, my face,
quickly.

1:25:15.806 --> 1:25:17.460
Why?

1:25:17.460 --> 1:25:19.810
Please, I'm not kidding. I
can't stand it.

1:25:19.810 --> 1:25:21.507
Why should I help you?

1:25:21.507 --> 1:25:23.640
For the love of God, Mike!

1:25:23.640 --> 1:25:25.424
What did you do, Anton?

1:25:25.424 --> 1:25:28.688
You must've done something
terrible to deserve all this.

1:25:28.688 --> 1:25:30.299
What did you do?

1:25:30.299 --> 1:25:32.605
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

1:25:32.605 --> 1:25:34.520
Confess, Anton!

1:25:34.520 --> 1:25:36.435
Have you gone mad?

1:25:36.435 --> 1:25:38.002
I'm begging you.

1:25:38.002 --> 1:25:40.309
Just for a moment.

1:25:40.309 --> 1:25:42.049
Just one scratch.

1:25:42.049 --> 1:25:44.400
Look at you.
You've lost everything you have.

1:25:44.400 --> 1:25:47.533
Your money, your love, your
self-respect.

1:25:47.533 --> 1:25:49.056
You're broken, Anton.

1:25:49.056 --> 1:25:50.493
You're repulsive!

1:25:51.885 --> 1:25:54.453
Is this what you want? Is this
enough?

1:25:54.453 --> 1:25:56.760
No, huh? You want more?

1:25:58.283 --> 1:25:59.502
All right.

1:26:01.330 --> 1:26:04.463
Do it, Anton. Confess.

1:26:04.463 --> 1:26:06.726
Confess what?

1:26:06.726 --> 1:26:07.988
That you hurt people!

1:26:07.988 --> 1:26:10.600
Who, Linda? Yes, I cheated on
Linda.

1:26:10.600 --> 1:26:14.386
I admit it, but why should you
care?

1:26:14.386 --> 1:26:15.822
You were using her, weren't you?

1:26:15.822 --> 1:26:17.781
What are you talking about?

1:26:17.781 --> 1:26:19.609
Just admit it!

1:26:19.609 --> 1:26:21.567
That you were using her
to stay in this country...

1:26:21.567 --> 1:26:23.874
...just the way you used Maggie!

1:26:38.845 --> 1:26:41.544
I never told you anything about
Maggie.

1:26:43.720 --> 1:26:45.765
Who the hell are you?

1:26:46.940 --> 1:26:49.378
I'm the Milky Way man...

1:26:49.378 --> 1:26:52.294
...and I know everything.

1:26:59.126 --> 1:27:01.259
You're going to hurt yourself.

1:27:06.917 --> 1:27:08.092
You're killing yourself.

1:27:08.092 --> 1:27:09.354
Here. Let me help you.

1:27:19.582 --> 1:27:22.802
How's this? You enjoying the
show?

1:28:31.436 --> 1:28:33.308
Maggie was my angel.

1:28:37.007 --> 1:28:40.489
She brought me here, in America.

1:28:40.489 --> 1:28:42.839
I was nothing before I met her.

1:28:42.839 --> 1:28:46.277
Just a waiter in a little café
in Paris.

1:28:49.846 --> 1:28:52.370
Yeah. I used her.

1:28:53.545 --> 1:28:55.373
I used her terribly.

1:28:56.548 --> 1:28:58.942
But I didn't think it
mattered...

1:29:00.117 --> 1:29:01.901
...because I was...

1:29:01.901 --> 1:29:05.209
...sure that I would grow to
love her.

1:29:08.081 --> 1:29:10.954
I thought if I could just love
her, then...

1:29:13.043 --> 1:29:15.045
...it would be all right.

1:29:17.917 --> 1:29:19.789
The shame would go away.

1:29:21.399 --> 1:29:23.967
You can't choose who you love,
Mike...

1:29:23.967 --> 1:29:26.578
...or whoever the hell you
are...

1:29:26.578 --> 1:29:28.624
...and I love Linda.

1:29:28.624 --> 1:29:30.234
I love Linda.

1:29:36.196 --> 1:29:37.981
More than anything!

1:29:47.991 --> 1:29:52.125
Who the hell do you think
you are to judge?

1:29:52.125 --> 1:29:54.563
Who the hell do you think you
are?

1:29:56.521 --> 1:29:58.088
I'm nobody, Anton.

1:30:01.439 --> 1:30:02.614
I'm nobody.

1:30:05.574 --> 1:30:08.098
Nobody to nobody.

1:30:44.482 --> 1:30:46.441
Linda, we need to talk.

1:30:56.189 --> 1:30:58.627
Hello? Yes, please.

1:30:58.627 --> 1:31:03.980
I need to be scratched on my
face,
my chest, and my back.

1:31:03.980 --> 1:31:05.547
Please. Hello?

1:31:08.245 --> 1:31:11.640
It is an emergency call. I
swear.

1:31:11.640 --> 1:31:13.511
Hello, mister?

1:31:59.078 --> 1:32:00.645
Say we're even.

1:32:00.645 --> 1:32:02.429
-What?
-Just say it.

1:32:05.302 --> 1:32:07.260
Yes, we are even.

1:32:07.260 --> 1:32:08.392
Good.

1:32:12.570 --> 1:32:14.180
So how ya been?

1:32:55.308 --> 1:32:58.311
Here! I'm here, Linda!

1:32:58.311 --> 1:33:00.357
Oh, baby! Look at you!

1:33:01.837 --> 1:33:03.534
Oh, God!

1:33:03.534 --> 1:33:06.450
Oh, honey!

1:33:06.450 --> 1:33:09.148
I love you.

1:33:09.148 --> 1:33:11.194
Everything's going to be okay.

1:34:18.783 --> 1:34:20.742
Bad dog! Go away!

1:35:27.809 --> 1:35:30.376
So I saw this episode of [WE]
Lassie[WE] today...

1:35:31.769 --> 1:35:35.251
...and Lassie was accused
of a crime she didn't commit...

1:35:36.905 --> 1:35:40.082
...and the ranger was coming
to put her to sleep.

1:35:42.084 --> 1:35:45.130
How's Lassie going to get out of
this one?

1:35:45.130 --> 1:35:49.787
Well, the little boy found out
that the ranger was coming...

1:35:49.787 --> 1:35:52.703
...and he told Lassie that...

1:35:52.703 --> 1:35:55.140
...that she had to go away, far
away.

1:35:55.140 --> 1:35:56.576
For her own good.

1:35:56.576 --> 1:35:59.841
But Lassie wouldn't leave.

1:35:59.841 --> 1:36:02.495
See, Lassie just couldn't leave
the boy.

1:36:04.628 --> 1:36:06.108
What did he do?

1:36:07.805 --> 1:36:09.764
He told her that he never liked
her.

1:36:09.764 --> 1:36:13.506
He said, "I hate you.

1:36:13.506 --> 1:36:16.509
"I hate you, Lassie. You're a
bad dog.

1:36:16.509 --> 1:36:18.511
"I hope I never see you again."

1:36:18.511 --> 1:36:21.123
That must have made Lassie sad.

1:36:21.123 --> 1:36:22.124
Yes, it did.

1:36:22.124 --> 1:36:24.517
Lassie trotted off...

1:36:24.517 --> 1:36:25.954
...very sadly.

1:36:28.347 --> 1:36:30.262
But you know what happened?

1:36:32.264 --> 1:36:34.571
Lassie came home, Maggie.

1:36:34.571 --> 1:36:37.269
Did the little boy make it with
Lassie?

1:36:40.664 --> 1:36:42.100
Yes, he did.

